videos.description: Oregon's Maite Cazorla goes coast to coast for the easy layup in front of family members who traveled from Spain to cheer her on.
videos.headline: Cazorla's family cheers after layup

videos.description: Michaela Onyenwere is greeted with a full-court pass from Kennedy Burke as Onyenwere puts in the easy basket and UCLA leads No. 2 Oregon.
